  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个任务调度系统的状态图。系统启动后先进入Initialized状态，等配置加载完成(config_loaded)后进入Ready状态。Ready里面要包含Idle和Busy两个子状态，还有错误处理机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initialized",
        "Ready",
        "config_loaded",
        "Idle",
        "Busy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Ready是一个复合状态。那Idle到Busy的转换条件是收到任务(task_received)吗？Busy完成任务后怎么返回Idle？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Busy",
        "task_received"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，task_received触发进入Busy。任务完成后用task_complete返回Idle。另外Busy执行失败时要转到Error状态，条件是task_failed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Busy",
        "Idle",
        "task_complete",
        "Error",
        "task_failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Error也做成复合状态，里面放Retrying和Failed。Retrying成功的话返回Idle，重试次数超限就到Failed。这样设计可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Retrying",
        "Failed",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，转换条件分别是retry_success和retry_limit。Failed状态需要能reset回Idle。还有，整个Ready状态要能响应stop_signal进入Shutdown。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Failed",
        "Idle",
        "reset",
        "Ready",
        "Shutdown",
        "stop_signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Shutdown状态，stop_signal触发从Ready转出。Shutdown是终止状态，指向结束节点。我检查一下复合状态的层级结构是否正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shutdown",
        "Ready",
        "stop_signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Error复合状态的入口有问题。Error的初始状态应该是Retrying，不是直接到Failed。你刚才可能把[*]指向搞错了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Retrying",
        "Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复，Error的[*]现在正确指向Retrying。整个结构确认：Ready包含Idle-Busy-Error子状态机，Error内部是Retrying→Idle/Failed，Failed可reset。Shutdown作为终止状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Retrying",
        "Ready",
        "Shutdown"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了。完整的流转是：系统启动→Initialized→Ready(Idle↔Busy，失败进Error重试)→Shutdown终止。所有边界条件都覆盖到了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initialized",
        "Ready",
        "Idle",
        "Busy",
        "Error",
        "Shutdown"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
